body: Harrison Butker said it best.͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏ ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏ ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏ ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  ͏  | | | ![](https://d15k2d11r6t6rl.cloudfront.net/public/users/Integrators/669d5713-9b6a-46bb-bd7e-c542cff6dd6a/dacf945cc62b4e24a89a6062cde01b6e/UPRIGHT.png) --- | ---  ![](https://d15k2d11r6t6rl.cloudfront.net/public/users/Integrators/669d5713-9b6a-46bb-bd7e-c542cff6dd6a/dacf945cc62b4e24a89a6062cde01b6e/3Sequence%2001.00_00_00_07.Still001-02.jpeg) ---  _“I’m supporting a President who’s the most pro-life President—and I thinkthat’s Donald Trump.”_  Harrison Butker said it best.  We need a Presidentwho will stand **STRONG** and **FIGHT** for the unborn, _someone who willstand up for the most vulnerable in our society._  The other side has made itclear—** _they want to push their agenda of abortion on demand, and they willdo whatever it takes to silence the pro-life movement. _** But we won’t letthem. --- ![](https://d15k2d11r6t6rl.cloudfront.net/public/users/Integrators/669d5713-9b6a-46bb-bd7e-c542cff6dd6a/dacf945cc62b4e24a89a6062cde01b6e/HawleyButkerStLouis-20241010AH-9304559.jpg) --- **STAND WITH HARRISON BUTKER, DEFEND LIFE** ---  President Trump has been the strongest defender of the unborn we’ve ever seenin the White House.  **He’s not afraid to stand up for life, and that’sexactly what our country needs right now.**  We should be fighting for themost vulnerable, fighting for the unborn.  If you are going to donate to anyorganization this cycle, it should be ours, we are mobilizing Christians tovote for **LIFE** in 2024. **That’s the future we’re fighting for.**  We areworking to mobilize voters of faith, but we need your help to keep up thefight.
